"Time to add a special touch to the winter season with @chai_point ’s latest food range! ❄❤️

Where do I begin? The Aloo Tikki Chaat and Samosa Chaat had the perfect combination of spicy and tangy, the Brownies were soft, fudgy, and gluten-free and to add a chatpata touch - I ordered some Bread Pakodas and they were crispy and binge-worthy! 😍💯

Want some delicious Winter treats? Then head on to your nearest Chai Point outlet and check out their food range today! 😃"

Reposted from @grubmode 
.

"Winter + Chai = PERFECTION!

I found out about @chai_point 's winter food range and couldn’t wait to give it a shot! 😃

The Aloo Tikki Chaat and Samosa Chaat had the perfect level of chatpata flavours, the Bread Pakodas were crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, the Pesto Paneer Croissant was lip-smackingly delicious, and the gluten-free Fudgy Brownies (my personal favourite) was absolutely heavenly. I couldn’t have asked for a better winter evening! 😍😋

Chai Point has always been my favourite hang-out spot and this new food range has given me all the more reason to check out their place more often. Make this winter memorable with Chai Point and let me know which product from the new menu you're most excited to try out! 💯☕"

Reposted from @funfoodandfrolic 
.

"Winters and Chai Point are a perfect mix! ☕❄️

We couldn’t wait to give @chai_point ‘s latest winter food range a shot and it was truly a delightful experience! 🤤

Stuffed with flavorful stuffing and tangy chutneys, the Samosa Chaat and Aloo Tikki Chaat were great accompaniments to their ever-ideal Chai 😍

The Pesto Paneer Croissant was mouthwatering and the Fudgy Brownies were irresistible. It’s astonishing to see a gluten-free dessert with a crackly exterior and a soft interior! 😋💯

Chai Point is the ideal winter spot for us and we’re in love with their latest food menu. Let me know which product you’re looking forward to trying! 😍💯"

"Winters and @chai_point are a match made in heaven! ❄️☕

I was stoked to check out Chai Point's newest winter food range and was amazed! The Egg & Cheese croissant was lip-smacking, the Bread Pakodas were crispy, light and filled with flavourful stuffing, the Samosa Binge Pack was a perfect addition to a night of watching the World Cup with friends, and who can forget the Fudgy Brownies! 🤤 A crackly crust, with a soft interior — something that is amazing to see in a gluten-free dessert! 😎

Chai Point has always been a great winter spot and with this new menu, it's definitely going to be where I spend my time! Let me know which product from the new menu you're most excited to try out! 😃"

"The Chai enthusiast in me is obsessed with winters and @chai_point 😋
I was stoked to check out their newest winter food range and it surpassed my expectations! 💯

The Aloo Tikki and Samosa Chaats were heavenly. They were a perfect combination of delicious tangy and spicy flavours! And the Bread Pakodas? They were crispy on the outside, soft on the inside and came with 2 chutneys. 

Lastly, how could I forget the FUDGY BROWNIE? My absolute favourite! It was rich, soft, loaded with chocolate and most importantly, GLUTEN-FREE! 😍😋

Chai Point is going to be my go-to hangout spot this winter! Make sure you head to the nearest store and add charm to the winter season! ❄️☕"

Reposted from @iamdatingfood 
.
